想法，可是处方粮我还是接着买了新的一袋，罐头又买了新的。看着猫又真的很来气，他为什么就不能省心一点呢。起码不要在床上尿。真的不想养了，但是送人我又怕养不好，我该怎么办"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-0f774d1437e1688f6425ca62cbee1806_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "54 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/660930373"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IgOXwrebA75BFEAMaCTEwOTE1MTA0MSCg+6W0BjAAOBxAGXIJNjYwOTMwMzczeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "26_1724041424.511728", "card_id": "Q_664386427", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 39}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如果一个人缺少人生阅历和情感体验，那这人是否能够成为一名作家?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-b8f432220a1471f9801c536c868fe5a6_1440w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "48 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/664386427"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIgOXwrebA75BFEAMaCTEwOTkxODk1MCDT7ve1BjAAOIIBQBpyCTY2NDM4NjQyN3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "27_1724041424.511966", "card_id": "Q_664308271", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 49}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "在自负与自卑之间横跳，无法正视自己怎么办？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "一直找不到一个平衡点，大多数时间沉浸在自卑和对自我的怀疑中。试图增加自信的时候，发现很容易自负怎么办？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-0b35d96c3d6990ed29d63962859b06d5_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "46 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/664308271"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIgOXwrebA75BFEAMaCTEwOTkwMTYxMCDnyPO1BjAAOJIBQBtyCTY2NDMwODI3MXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type"